column2: SELECT up_id,  dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) as SpecobjId   FROM #upload  WHERE  dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjIdEq( up_ra,up_dec,up_sep ) IS NOT NULL  SELECT TOP #   s.ra,s.dec,s.class,s.z,s.zWarning,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,p.modelMagErr_u,p.modelMagErr_g,p.modelMagErr_r,p.modelMagErr_i,p.modelMagErr_z,p.psfMag_u,p.psfMag_g,p.psfMag_r,p.psfMag_i,p.psfMag_z,p.psfMagErr_u,p.psfMagErr_g,p.psfMagErr_r,p.psfMagErr_i,p.psfMagErr_z  FROM ..SpecObj as s  JOIN ..PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  JOIN #x AS x ON x.SpecobjID=s.SpecobjID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  s.zWarning = # AND ( p.type = # OR p.type = #)   ORDER BY x.up_id
